{"pageProps":{"post":{"title":"알고리즘 - 문자열을 정수로 바꾸기","date":"2020-01-09","slug":"2020-01-09-algorithm-14","content":"<h4>문제설명</h4>\n<p>문자열 s를 숫자로 변환한 결과를 반환하는 함수, solution을 완성하세요.</p>\n<br>\n<h4>제한사항</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>s의 길이는 1 이상 5이하입니다.</li>\n<li>s의 맨앞에는 부호(+, -)가 올 수 있습니다.</li>\n<li>s는 부호와 숫자로만 이루어져있습니다.</li>\n<li>s는 0으로 시작하지 않습니다.</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<h4><strong>풀이</strong></h4>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"javascript\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">function</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">solution</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75; font-style: italic\">s</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">) {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">return</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">parseInt</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">s</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ol>\n<li><code>parseInt</code>를 사용하여 정수로 변환</li>\n</ol>\n<br>\n<h4><strong>다른 사람 풀이</strong></h4>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"javascript\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"javascript\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">function</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #61AFEF\">strToInt</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">(</span><span style=\"color: #E06C75; font-style: italic\">str</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">) {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C678DD\">return</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">str</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #56B6C2\">/</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">1</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<ol>\n<li>매개변수에 연산자를 나눠주었다.</li>\n</ol>\n<br>\n<h4><strong>배운점</strong></h4>\n<p>왜 나온 문제인지 이해가 안가지만 괜히 꼬인 문제인가 계속 쳐다봤다.<br>\n하지만 바로 풀어버림;; 당황쓰..</p>\n<p><br><br><br><br><br></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><subtitle>reference</subtitle></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://tutorial.djangogirls.org/ko\">https://tutorial.djangogirls.org/ko</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://blog.daum.net/_blog/BlogTypeView.do?blogid=0QtKg&#x26;articleno=28&#x26;categoryId=0&#x26;totalcnt=30\">http://blog.daum.net/_blog/BlogTypeView.do?blogid=0QtKg&#x26;articleno=28&#x26;categoryId=0&#x26;totalcnt=30</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br><br><br><br><br></p>","coverImage":"/assets/blog/cover/algorithm.jpg"}},"__N_SSG":true}